190 The board shall have the power and responsibility to:
191 (1) Determine the qualifications and fitness of applicants for licensure and renewal of
192 licensure;
193 (2) Adopt and revise rules consistent with the laws of the State of Georgia that are
194 necessary to conduct its business, carry out its duties, and administer this article;
